  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nIf you want to install a plugin-in (new in 5.0.0-beta2), you have to configure it for each truffle project.\r\n\r\nShouldn't there be a way to specify it globally? \r\n\r\nLet's say I want to add verification to my Smart Contracts and there's a plugin that does that. I'm not sure why I'd want to have that available for some of my truffle projects but not all of them.",
